high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter with the microwave on it on the right.
Pick up the salt shaker from the counter to the left of the microwave.
Turn around and face the cabinet below the counter with the loaf of bread on it.
Open the cabinet door, place the salt shaker inside the cabinet, close the door.
Turn around and walk back to the counter with the microwave on it.
Pick up another salt shaker to the left of the microwave.
Walk back over to the cabinet below the counter.
Open the cabinet door, put the salt shaker in the cabinet to the left of the first one, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: To move two salt shakers to the cabinet.

Turn around, go forward to the counter.
Put the salt mill in the bottom cabinet to the left of the green bin.
Turn around, go back to the dresser with the microwave.
Take the salt mill closest to the wall from the dresser.
Turn around, go forward to the counter.
Put the salt mill in the bottom cabinet to the left of the first salt mill.
anns.task_desc: Put two salt mills in a cabinet.
